      ],
      "id": "b736e879-b304-ee23-437d-c91b19364198",
      "name": "Note: Approved?"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Apply Approved Change (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token",
        "width": 280,
