    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Record Decline + Notify Requester\n\nmicrosoftTeams — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
        "color": 2
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
